The parser receives raw PDF **bytes** (`io.BytesIO`) — not a path — per the stateless ingestion contract in `INGEST.md`. It never writes to disk. The `announcement_date` is supplied by the caller (the ASX API metadata already includes it — there is no reason to re-parse it from the PDF).

